flowchart TD
    RAW[Raw Data Captured] --> VALIDATE{Validation Engine}

    VALIDATE -->|Glucose| G_CHECK{Reading valid?}
    G_CHECK -->|Anomaly / Gap| FLAG[Flag for review]
    G_CHECK -->|Valid| STORE_G[Store in Time-Series DB]

    VALIDATE -->|Food| F_CHECK{Entry complete?}
    F_CHECK -->|Missing info| PROMPT[Prompt patient]
    F_CHECK -->|Complete| STORE_F[Store in Patient DB]

    STORE_G --> CORRELATE[Correlation Engine]
    STORE_F --> CORRELATE

    CORRELATE --> RESULT[Correlation Result]
    RESULT --> FEEDBACK{Patient / Clinician confirms?}
    FEEDBACK -->|Confirmed| LEARN[Improve model]
    FEEDBACK -->|Rejected| ADJUST[Re-correlate]
    ADJUST --> CORRELATE
